NOTE on Source Data:

This project uses subtitle data derived from publicly available educational
videos by Bilibili content creator "一化儿" (Yihuier / "Jiege"). The use of
this data falls under non-commercial educational research and personal
learning tool development.

The trained system_prompt and answer-formatting templates are derivative
expressions inspired by Yihuier's teaching methodology. While the code
framework is licensed under MIT, users are kindly asked NOT to repurpose the
specific Jiege-style prompts for commercial products, as this would be
commercial exploitation of an educator's teaching style without consent.

If Yihuier or their legal representatives have any concerns about this
project, please reach out via GitHub Issues for prompt resolution.
